OL,4,CGerry Marsden: Statue planned for
OL,5,CLiverpool FC anthem singer
OL,6, A statue of Gerry and the Pacemakers
OL,7, singer Gerry Marsden could be built on
OL,8, Liverpool's waterfront.
OL,10,FSculptor Laura Lian wanted to honour
OL,11,Fthe singer whose version of You'll
OL,12,FNever Walk Alone became a terrace
OL,13,Fanthem for his hometown club Liverpool.
OL,15,FMarsden, who was made an MBE in 2003,
OL,16,Fdied after a short illness on 3 January
OL,17,Fat the age of 78.
OL,19,FThe statue could overlook the river he
OL,20,Fimmortalised in his classic hit, Ferry
OL,21,FCross The Mersey.
